Class AnimatingViewportState

Namespace
FlowGraph.Avalonia.Input.States
Assembly
FlowGraph.Avalonia.dll

Input state active during viewport animations (pan/zoom transitions). Allows cancellation via click or key press, and permits zoom wheel interactions.

public class AnimatingViewportState : InputStateBase, IInputState
